    "longBusinessSummary": "ST8 Holdings Joint Stock Company focuses on the agriculture and real-estate businesses in Vietnam. The company engages in the management consulting activities; wholesale of agricultural and forestry products, raw materials, and live animals; and retail sale of computers, peripheral equipment, and software and telecommunication equipment in specialized stores. It is also involved in the manufacture of computers and peripheral equipment; communication equipment; consumer electronics; and motorcycles, generators, electrical transformers, and electrical distribution and control apparatus, as well as wholesale of household goods; agricultural machinery, equipment, and parts; and other specialized goods. In addition, the company repairs machinery and equipment, computers and peripheral equipment, consumer electronics, and communications equipment; constructs buildings of various types; installs building systems; and rents machinery, equipment, and other tangible goods. Further, it is involved in the agency, brokerage, and auction services; financial and advertising services; real estate activities with owned, used, or leased land use rights; cashew nut, coffee, and other perennial crop farming; mixed farming of crops and livestock; crop production and post-harvest services; inland aquaculture and grain milling services; production of crude flour and smart industrial products; trading and investment activities; securities investment funds; and processing and preserving of fish, crustaceans, molluscs, and other aquatic animal products, as well as fruits and vegetables. The company was formerly known as Sieu Thanh Joint Stock Corporation and changed its name to ST8 Holdings Joint Stock Company in July 2024. ST8 Holdings Joint Stock Company was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
